io.nem.symbol.sdk.model.account

Enum AccountKeyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AccountKeyType>
      • io.nem.symbol.sdk.model.account.AccountKeyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AccountKeyType>

    public enum AccountKeyType
extends java.lang.Enum<AccountKeyType>
    Type of account key: * 0 - Unset. * 1 - Linked account public key. * 2 - Node public key on which remote is allowed to harvest. * 4 - VRF public key.
